1
00:02:10,940 --> 00:02:15,620
- Renegade Immortal -

2
00:02:33,060 --> 00:02:38,980
(Copyright Statement)

3
00:02:38,980 --> 00:02:40,340
(Minors Should Watch Only
with the Consent of Their Guardians)

4
00:02:40,340 --> 00:02:41,820
(This Film is Entirely Fictional)

5
00:02:41,820 --> 00:02:43,340
(Including cultivation systems
and all mystical powers)

6
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:44,900
(Please Do Not Imitate in Real Life)

7
00:02:45,420 --> 00:02:50,340
(Adapted from Er Gen's
"Renegade Immortal" on Qidian)

8
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,690
(Previously on...)
(In just ten years,)

9
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:55,400
(my soul is fully restored.)

10
00:02:55,910 --> 00:02:57,110
(This body)

11
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:59,040
(holds lightning power.)

12
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,360
(It proves)

13
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,520
(the Dao has not doomed me.)

14
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,980
(The Fatebreaker Pearl
was already full of mysteries.)

15
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:07,520
(Now that it's complete,
it's even harder to grasp.)

16
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:10,120
(To break my Dao intent
with a mere gate?)

17
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:11,990
(Dream on!)

18
00:03:12,580 --> 00:03:16,010
(Let me see
what truly lies within this gate.)

19
00:03:16,780 --> 00:03:17,930
Do you know

20
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,640
what is Dao?

21
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,920
(At the end of seeking the Dao,)

22
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,000
(one seeks oneself.)

23
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,240
(That figure...)

24
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:26,640
(Who is it?)

25
00:03:29,460 --> 00:03:34,420
Episode 146
[Commanding Thunder]
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

26
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,990
(The Thunder Immortal Realm
is about to open.)

27
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,170
(This time,)

28
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:13,000
(inside the Thunder Pool,)

29
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:15,200
(I must refine as much
of my origin power as I can.)

30
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:18,510
(This...)

31
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,000
(is pressure.)

32
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,780
(Did something happen
to the Thunder Pool?)

33
00:04:28,130 --> 00:04:29,330
(A Silver-Horned Thunder Beast)

34
00:04:29,990 --> 00:04:31,190
(and a Yin Void Puppet?)

35
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:32,920
(Wait...)

36
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,470
(Is he a Lightning Immortal Envoy too?)

37
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,660
(He's only an Ascension cultivator.)

38
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,940
(How is he staying there
like the Thunder Pool is nothing?)

39
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:03,800
(With just one glance,)

40
00:05:04,410 --> 00:05:06,210
(Shengong Hu, Lightning Immortal Envoy)
(he wounded my mind,)

41
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,600
(Yin Void, fallen from Yang Real)
(shook my Dao heart,)

42
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:10,200
(and sent my cultivation plummeting
to Yin Void.)

43
00:05:11,780 --> 00:05:13,100
(So the Fatebreaker Pearl)

44
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:16,680
(actually holds a monstrous chance
to reach the third step?)

45
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:19,640
(I only glimpsed a crack today,)

46
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,160
(and already gained this much.)

47
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:23,690
(If that gate ever fully opens,)

48
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,840
(I dare not even imagine it.)

49
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:30,520
(The gaze that nearly shattered my mind)

50
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:33,080
(must have been
the legendary Dao nightmare.)

51
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,200
(If I can follow him,)

52
00:05:35,730 --> 00:05:38,940
(it would be the fortune of a lifetime.)

53
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,690
Greetings, Senior.

54
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,080
What do you want?

55
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:44,240
Senior,

56
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,680
my name is Shengong Hu.

57
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:48,180
I'm from the Shen Gong Clan
of Southern Domain

58
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:50,410
and a second-rank
Lightning Immortal Envoy.

59
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,520
I was once at the Yang Real stage.

60
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,040
I beg you, please let me serve you.

61
00:05:55,550 --> 00:05:56,590
Serve me?

62
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,600
I know...

63
00:05:58,610 --> 00:06:00,450
- (Is he saying this)
- my cultivation is weak.

64
00:06:00,450 --> 00:06:02,080
- (because of my insight)
- I'm not worthy to serve you.

65
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,560
- (scared him into submission?)
- But

66
00:06:03,700 --> 00:06:05,390
many cultivation clans answer to me.

67
00:06:05,420 --> 00:06:06,450
(But I may never be able)

68
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,580
- (to use that insight again.)
- Whatever you need,

69
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:11,490
- (Shengong Hu used to be Yang Real.)
- I can be useful to you.

70
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,690
- (If he ever sees through me,)
- My loyalty is sincere.

71
00:06:13,690 --> 00:06:14,400
I swear to heaven.

72
00:06:14,430 --> 00:06:15,280
(I'll be in serious danger.)

73
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:16,110
All I ask

74
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,570
is for a few words of guidance
when I break through.

75
00:06:19,030 --> 00:06:19,820
No.

76
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:25,690
Senior,

77
00:06:26,350 --> 00:06:27,960
I'll offer you my Dao soul.

78
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:29,000
I swear it on my Dao heart.

79
00:06:29,910 --> 00:06:32,170
Please let me serve you
for a thousand years.

80
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,660
He's even offering his Dao soul?

81
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,270
(Once I have his Dao soul,)

82
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,620
(I won't have to fear betrayal.)

83
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,720
(He's quite decisive.)

84
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,610
You will not regret this?

85
00:06:46,250 --> 00:06:47,630
Never.

86
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,260
Why are you here?

87
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,270
The Thunder Immortal Realm
will open soon.

88
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:57,040
I came here to cultivate

89
00:06:57,070 --> 00:06:58,080
and absorb origin power.

90
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,470
I'm not from Luotian.

91
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:04,220
How long
before the Thunder Immortal Realm opens?

92
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:05,770
Thirty years.

93
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:08,570
When the time comes,
a Thunder Cauldron can take you inside.

94
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,830
(Thirty years?)

95
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,110
(The Rain Immortal Realm back then)

96
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:15,450
(laid the foundation for my battles
across the stars.)

97
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,470
(Now, this Thunder Immortal Realm)

98
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:21,630
(is somewhere I must go,
no matter what.)

99
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:25,110
Does the Thunder Immortal Realm

100
00:07:25,660 --> 00:07:27,060
have any cultivation restrictions?

101
00:07:28,380 --> 00:07:28,990
Senior,

102
00:07:29,620 --> 00:07:31,530
anyone at peak late-stage Ascendant
or below

103
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,640
can enter.

104
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,900
With the Lightning Immortal Temple's
secret art,

105
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,640
even the second step cultivators

106
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:37,890
can go inside.

107
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,520
But once inside,

108
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:42,610
no one can use divine techniques
beyond early Nirvana Glimpse.

109
00:07:43,010 --> 00:07:43,740
Otherwise,

110
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,650
the realm will collapse.

111
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,820
(Then...)

112
00:07:58,660 --> 00:07:59,610
(Seventy steps?)

113
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,610
(Eighty steps?)

114
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:03,780
(Ninety-five steps?)

115
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:06,970
(One hundred steps?)

116
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,080
(One hundred steps in,)

117
00:08:09,090 --> 00:08:10,660
(and the thunder means nothing to him.)

118
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:13,760
(Senior really is a hidden master.)

119
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:15,990
(I, Shengong Hu,)

120
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:17,720
(made the right bet.)

121
00:08:35,580 --> 00:08:36,750
(Ten steps...)

122
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:39,040
(Right now,)

123
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:41,800
(ten steps is my limit?)

124
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:47,120
(If I were at full strength,)

125
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:50,100
(fifty steps would not be a problem.)

126
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,800
(In my battle with Lei Daozi,)

127
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:59,140
(I overused the Net-Severing Sword Art.)

128
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:01,980
(It nearly drained my origin power dry.)

129
00:09:03,210 --> 00:09:04,270
(At the first step,)

130
00:09:04,860 --> 00:09:06,840
(recovering origin power
is painfully difficult.)

131
00:09:07,500 --> 00:09:09,180
(Fortunately,
I have the lightning soul.)

132
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:13,670
(With the Lightning Essence Art,
I can turn it into origin power.)

133
00:09:14,180 --> 00:09:15,770
(I need to recover as fast as possible.)

134
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:17,720
(At one hundred steps,)

135
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:19,800
(he's pulling that much thunder
into his body?)

136
00:09:20,650 --> 00:09:21,510
(If I tried that,)

137
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,640
(my soul would be crippled.)

138
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:25,730
(Senior's cultivation)

139
00:09:26,420 --> 00:09:27,690
(is beyond anything I can read.)

140
00:09:31,660 --> 00:09:35,380
(Two Years Later)

141
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:38,120
(The thunder near the edge)

142
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:40,800
(is still too weak and impure.)

143
00:09:41,680 --> 00:09:42,760
(Only deeper inside)

144
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:45,910
(can I refine truly pure origin power.)

145
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,400
(If I want to recover faster,)

146
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,350
(I have to go deeper.)

147
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:52,720
(He moved.)

148
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,720
(Senior is finally moving again.)

149
00:09:55,700 --> 00:09:56,840
(I waited two years)

150
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,550
(just for this exact moment.)

151
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:02,000
(If I can catch even a trace
of his divine technique,)

152
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:04,120
(it will be a blessing from heaven.)

153
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,290
(The thunder pressure here)

154
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,160
(is terrifying.)

155
00:10:58,820 --> 00:10:59,950
(Ten steps?)

156
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,530
(Senior finally moved again,)

157
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:24,000
(but only ten steps?)

158
00:11:25,680 --> 00:11:27,120
(That terrifying aura before...)

159
00:11:27,150 --> 00:11:28,410
(Was it just luck?)

160
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,360
(Then my pledge)

161
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,760
(would be a complete joke.)

162
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:37,760
(Brute force will not get me through.)

163
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:40,560
(My soul and thunder
share the same source.)

164
00:11:41,140 --> 00:11:42,700
(There has to be a way in.)

165
00:11:49,700 --> 00:11:51,180
(Even the same source was rejected?)

166
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:52,720
(Could it be)

167
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,520
(not about power,)

168
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:56,880
(but Dao?)

169
00:11:57,560 --> 00:11:58,880
(All things in heaven and earth)

170
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,880
(begin within the self.)

171
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,320
(It's not about using power.)

172
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:06,600
(It's about becoming one with the Dao.)

173
00:12:07,660 --> 00:12:09,800
(Only when the Dao aligns
can the source be absorbed.)

174
00:12:09,824 --> 00:12:27,624
(Watch the Latest Donoghue Episodes: www.h-donghua.com)

175
00:12:28,930 --> 00:12:29,500
He...

176
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:31,080
He's walking on thunder!

177
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:32,980
The lightning itself becomes his path.

178
00:12:33,170 --> 00:12:34,310
Heaven and earth welcome him.

179
00:12:35,090 --> 00:12:37,230
This is the true peak
of the Lightning Dao.

180
00:12:38,410 --> 00:12:39,780
I waited two years

181
00:12:40,210 --> 00:12:41,030
just to witness

182
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:43,550
a divine power like this.

183
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:47,780
(That fleeting insight
into the third step)

184
00:12:48,230 --> 00:12:49,510
(and the understanding of Dao)

185
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:51,920
(may not be confrontational,)

186
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:54,480
(but it's more valuable)

187
00:12:54,900 --> 00:12:56,290
(than countless divine techniques.)

188
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:05,510
Well...

189
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,920
this place is lively.

190
00:13:12,700 --> 00:13:13,740
Zhan Konglie?

191
00:13:15,300 --> 00:13:17,980
(Zhan Konglie, Lightning Immortal Envoy,
Yang Real)

192
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,560
(Late-stage Ascension,)

193
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,960
(yet he can sit in the inner ring?)

194
00:13:24,560 --> 00:13:28,050
(He must have a treasure
blocking the thunder.)

195
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:30,200
You don't belong here.

196
00:13:30,310 --> 00:13:31,100
Get lost!

197
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:33,880
Well, well.

198
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,600
Shengong Hu.

199
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:37,440
Forgive my poor eyes.

200
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:39,240
I almost did not recognize you.

201
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,000
Your cultivation

202
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,880
has fallen quite a bit.

203
00:13:43,010 --> 00:13:44,120
None of your business!

204
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:47,240
This young man looks unfamiliar.

205
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:49,160
To sit safely in the inner ring,

206
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:51,600
you must have quite the treasure on you.

207
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:53,300
Why not show it to me?

208
00:13:53,400 --> 00:13:55,120
Let me broaden my horizons.

209
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,400
Master!

210
00:13:56,420 --> 00:13:57,080
This is bad!

211
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,400
We're in real trouble.

212
00:13:58,400 --> 00:13:59,600
He came looking for a fight.

213
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:00,840
If he sees through us,

214
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:03,670
we're finished.

215
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:05,440
(A Yang Real cultivator...)

216
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:08,200
(He thinks I have a powerful treasure.)

217
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:10,560
(He'll not let this go.)

218
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,080
(To prove his loyalty,)

219
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:15,480
(Shengong Hu will defend me
at all costs.)

220
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:18,400
(Before, we were evenly matched,)

221
00:14:18,800 --> 00:14:20,320
(so I had to play along.)

222
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:22,760
(But with my Lord here today,)

223
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:24,640
(why should I fear him?)

224
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,640
You have three breaths.

225
00:14:26,930 --> 00:14:27,780
Leave

226
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,000
or die!

227
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:33,160
(Fight me to the death)

228
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:35,260
(over some Ascension junior
with a treasure?)

229
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:37,120
(Shengong Hu,)

230
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:39,640
(what are you really planning?)

231
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,160
Zhan Konglie!

232
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:48,320
Die!

233
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:51,040
Gladly.

234
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:52,800
Let me see

235
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,800
what you are really hiding.

236
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:05,960
They're fighting!

237
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:08,280
Shengong Hu's cultivation has dropped.

238
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:09,800
He cannot last long!

239
00:15:10,560 --> 00:15:11,920
(If Shengong Hu loses,)

240
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:14,240
(I'll fall into Zhan Konglie's hands.)

241
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,480
(If I back down now,)

242
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:18,480
(Shengong Hu will grow suspicious.)

243
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:20,640
(Either way, I'm in danger.)

244
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:30,520
Shengong Hu,

245
00:15:31,280 --> 00:15:32,950
I'll not help you in this fight.

246
00:15:33,680 --> 00:15:35,620
Consider this your trial.

247
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,240
If you lose,

248
00:15:37,730 --> 00:15:39,210
I'll return your Dao soul.

249
00:15:40,230 --> 00:15:41,200
Don't worry, my Lord.

250
00:15:41,800 --> 00:15:43,440
I'll not disappoint you.

251
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:45,120
My Lord?

252
00:15:46,980 --> 00:15:48,520
To keep the treasure for yourself,

253
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:51,720
you two are putting
on this pathetic act?

254
00:15:52,190 --> 00:15:54,170
You think that will scare me away?

255
00:15:54,830 --> 00:15:55,790
What a joke.

256
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:26,770
(His thunder-summoning art is strong.)

257
00:16:27,500 --> 00:16:29,520
(He uses origin power
to draw on heaven and earth.)

258
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:32,420
(It nearly rivals forming a cauldron
from origin power.)

259
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:34,560
(But as the power moves,)

260
00:16:34,900 --> 00:16:36,320
(something is missing.)

261
00:16:37,640 --> 00:16:40,030
(There's a flaw hidden in its rhythm.)

262
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:46,320
(There it is...)

263
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:47,960
(the way out.)

264
00:17:17,270 --> 00:17:17,960
Go!

265
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:48,000
I have never liked you.

266
00:17:48,630 --> 00:17:49,690
But after today,

267
00:17:50,360 --> 00:17:51,580
I admit you have some skill.

268
00:17:52,520 --> 00:17:53,810
Shengong Hu,

269
00:17:54,320 --> 00:17:56,860
your divine technique
may carry thunder's might,

270
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:59,100
but it lacks its true essence.

271
00:18:00,280 --> 00:18:02,440
Your Dao heart is not one with thunder.

272
00:18:02,800 --> 00:18:05,660
How can you command
true lightning power?

273
00:18:07,460 --> 00:18:08,320
My Lord, you're right.

274
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:10,240
That is exactly where I'm stuck.

275
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:12,200
Please guide me, my Lord.

276
00:18:13,790 --> 00:18:15,220
Merge one's Dao intent with thunder?

277
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:16,560
Everyone knows that.

278
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:18,600
But the path forward is unclear.

279
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:20,840
No one knows how to do it.

280
00:18:21,560 --> 00:18:23,550
Anyone can talk in riddles.

281
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,360
Still pretending?

282
00:18:25,550 --> 00:18:27,420
Let see how you get out of this.

283
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:56,880
Do you understand now?

284
00:18:57,840 --> 00:18:59,120
(Strip away the surface.)

285
00:18:59,920 --> 00:19:01,280
(Go straight to the source.)

286
00:19:02,530 --> 00:19:04,300
(Only this can break the deadlock,)

287
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:06,880
(win without fighting,)

288
00:19:07,600 --> 00:19:09,200
(and force Zhan Konglie to retreat.)

289
00:19:09,470 --> 00:19:11,520
(He actually grasped
the source of the Dao?)

290
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:14,480
(No wonder Shengong Hu's Dao heart)

291
00:19:15,020 --> 00:19:16,380
(advanced in an instant.)

292
00:19:17,350 --> 00:19:18,690
(This man is no Ascension.)

293
00:19:19,180 --> 00:19:20,840
(His true cultivation
is beyond measure.)

294
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:22,760
My Lord, your guidance

295
00:19:23,080 --> 00:19:24,200
has given me a second life.

296
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:25,080
I...

297
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:26,760
understand.

298
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:28,320
Zhan Konglie!

299
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:29,640
Again!

300
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:34,640
I, Zhan Konglie, failed to recognize you.

301
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:36,590
I disturbed your cultivation, Senior.

302
00:19:36,600 --> 00:19:37,720
Please forgive my offense.

303
00:19:40,320 --> 00:19:41,560
Congratulations, Shengong Hu.

304
00:19:42,040 --> 00:19:43,300
You have found a worthy master.

305
00:19:43,520 --> 00:19:44,280
This is truly

306
00:19:44,560 --> 00:19:45,880
a heaven-sent fortune.

307
00:19:46,840 --> 00:19:48,400
I'm truly convinced.

308
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:51,680
I have received a summons
from the Lightning Immortal Temple.

309
00:19:52,160 --> 00:19:54,520
In the future,
we may serve there together as envoys.

310
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:55,820
Until then.

311
00:19:58,680 --> 00:20:00,680
My Lord, sorry for disturbing you.

312
00:20:01,160 --> 00:20:02,360
What summons?

313
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:06,080
My Lord, it's an order
from the Lightning Immortal Temple.

314
00:20:06,760 --> 00:20:08,400
Anyone chosen as a candidate

315
00:20:08,680 --> 00:20:09,520
will receive one.

316
00:20:10,120 --> 00:20:11,950
Three months before its opening,

317
00:20:12,600 --> 00:20:14,280
candidates compete to fill

318
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:16,920
any remaining envoy seats
that are vacant.

319
00:20:17,560 --> 00:20:18,820
With Zhan Konglie's cultivation,

320
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:21,240
he's likely to secure a seat

321
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:23,480
unless something unforeseen happens.

322
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:25,560
(If Shengong Hu stays here,)

323
00:20:26,080 --> 00:20:27,790
(he may attract more trouble.)

324
00:20:28,840 --> 00:20:30,360
I'll enter seclusion for a while

325
00:20:30,380 --> 00:20:32,120
to comprehend
an important divine technique.

326
00:20:32,970 --> 00:20:34,230
You should leave for now.

327
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:35,680
This is a message jade slip.

328
00:20:36,040 --> 00:20:37,120
Whenever you call,

329
00:20:37,840 --> 00:20:39,480
I'll come immediately.

330
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:40,960
This jade slip also contains

331
00:20:41,280 --> 00:20:43,280
a detailed star map
of the Southern Domain.

332
00:20:43,960 --> 00:20:46,040
It may help you find your way, My Lord.

333
00:20:48,120 --> 00:20:48,720
Go.

334
00:21:02,580 --> 00:21:06,300
(Eight Years Later)

335
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:11,770
(After ten years of refining,)

336
00:21:12,320 --> 00:21:13,880
(my soul is complete.)

337
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:17,160
(I cannot absorb any more origin power.)

338
00:21:17,760 --> 00:21:19,720
(I have reached a bottleneck.)

339
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:22,200
(If I want to go further,)

340
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:24,600
(I must break through the second step.)

341
00:21:26,660 --> 00:21:28,120
(The Five Elements are now complete.)

342
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:31,040
(But Yin and Yang remain split apart.)

343
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:33,180
(What does that mean?)

344
00:21:34,030 --> 00:21:34,940
(Fatebreaker Pearl,)

345
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:36,900
(what do you need)

346
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:39,280
(for the next step?)

347
00:21:41,420 --> 00:21:42,180
(Thankfully,)

348
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:44,790
(Muwan and the others' divine souls
are unharmed.)

349
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:47,800
(They even seem more stable
than before.)

350
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:52,040
(The Thunder Immortal Realm opens
in twenty years.)

351
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:53,760
(Right now,)

352
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:55,600
(breaking through comes first.)

353
00:21:57,080 --> 00:21:58,320
(Southern Domain)

354
00:21:58,880 --> 00:22:00,480
(has many abandoned planets.)

355
00:22:00,680 --> 00:22:01,880
(Mortals live there.)

356
00:22:02,880 --> 00:22:04,600
(They are perfect for hiding)

357
00:22:04,600 --> 00:22:05,800
(and cultivating in peace.)

358
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:09,080
(I need to find a safe base soon.)

359
00:22:10,600 --> 00:22:11,600
(It's time)

360
00:22:12,880 --> 00:22:16,360
(to claim a cultivation planet
of my own.)

361
00:22:20,560 --> 00:22:22,310
(Renegade Immortal: Thunder Immortal Realm Rising)
Immortal arts are mysterious.

362
00:22:22,800 --> 00:22:24,400
They can command the wind and rain

363
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:26,830
and turn beans into soldiers.

364
00:22:27,680 --> 00:22:29,640
No matter how precious the immortal art,

365
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:32,250
you must claim it
with your own strength.

366
00:22:32,810 --> 00:22:34,440
Do not let your master's techniques

367
00:22:35,260 --> 00:22:36,930
fade away in your hands.

368
00:23:16,690 --> 00:23:17,610
Ask

369
00:23:18,010 --> 00:23:19,810
(Qi Condensation)

370
00:23:21,450 --> 00:23:23,090
(Foundation Establishment)

371
00:23:24,010 --> 00:23:26,410
(Core Formation)

372
00:23:27,330 --> 00:23:29,850
(Nascent Soul)

373
00:23:30,850 --> 00:23:33,250
(Soul Formation)

374
00:23:33,650 --> 00:23:36,010
(Soul Transformation)

375
00:23:36,010 --> 00:23:37,970
And turn the tide of the stars

376
00:23:39,890 --> 00:23:42,450
(Ascension)

377
00:23:42,450 --> 00:23:47,490
Constantly refreshing the rules

378
00:23:49,050 --> 00:23:54,970
Rehearsing every possible outcome

379
00:23:55,290 --> 00:24:00,650
Once resolve is born,
right and wrong no longer matter

380
00:24:00,650 --> 00:24:08,170
Cutting free from every shackle
without hesitation

381
00:24:09,250 --> 00:24:12,650
A soul that breaks away
from mediocrity

382
00:24:12,650 --> 00:24:16,410
Forged by loneliness and resilience

383
00:24:16,410 --> 00:24:20,650
One more step
and it's the edge of the abyss

384
00:24:22,570 --> 00:24:25,890
Don't fall

385
00:24:25,890 --> 00:24:29,610
Look toward the summit

386
00:24:29,610 --> 00:24:34,730
Chase it

387
00:24:36,130 --> 00:24:42,810
Tempered and forged into perfection

388
00:24:55,650 --> 00:24:59,010
Through countless trials,
never retreating

389
00:24:59,010 --> 00:25:02,690
Daring to defy the will of heaven

390
00:25:02,690 --> 00:25:07,250
Shattering every barrier
on the path ahead

391
00:25:08,850 --> 00:25:12,250
Igniting the seas with blood

392
00:25:12,250 --> 00:25:15,970
Blooming through relentless refinement

393
00:25:15,970 --> 00:25:21,370
No matter how sharp these thorns

394
00:25:22,530 --> 00:25:29,610
Let everything turn to ash

395
00:25:29,634 --> 00:25:51,434
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

